{"tid":1357662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以暴易暴既始作俑者","createTime":"2019-07-23T18:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T05:13:48.000Z","uid":261343,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a5c8b316ff704c7a1fdc4b23f39a7bad88dfe057","tid":1357662,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:28:40.000Z","msg":"義士跟本係<br />\n以命易暴權<br />\n全部係揾自己條命<br />\n自己既將來<br />\n去換香港既未來<br />\n<br />\n以暴易暴既始作俑者<br />\n係林屎奠你<br />\n用警察既強力武力鎮壓示威者<br />\n再叫班黑社會用殺人既方法恐嚇示威者<br />\n<br />\n未見過有人好似你咁賤格<br />\n正人渣<br />\n正仆街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91bd0974a679db4769dd651f7b51eb3741f5fcbf","tid":1357662,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:31:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"ab2fbae90b374764fa95711d3184c98715024997","tid":1357662,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:32:50.000Z","msg":"嬲到訓唔着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee98d00bdb5bc668f14b2a97066e2284477e9c08","tid":1357662,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3